# Monorepo Rules

## Package Boundaries
- `apps/*` → can import `packages/*`
- `packages/*` → NEVER import `apps/*`
- Always import by package name, not relative path

## Naming Convention
`@repo/<specific-name>` — be descriptive, no catch-all `utils`

## Turborepo Pipeline
`build` depends on `^build` · `test` depends on `^build` · `lint` is independent
